  "texts": [
    "The tight coupling characteristic of Centaurian systems enables fluid interactions for complex tasks that require human judgment alongside AI-driven analysis.",
    "As agentic AI systems grow more sophisticated, the interplay between these paradigms becomes more dynamic.",
    "For instance, an enterprise AI system might operate independently (multi-agent mode) for routine tasks while tightly integrating with human experts (Centaurian mode) for complex decisions.",
    "Our framework supports the understanding and design of such interactions.",
    "Additionally, the \"data flywheel\" effect-continuous learning and adaptation-aligns with our model's emphasis on system evolution."
  ],
